Package: SunEditoR
Title: Wrapper for the SunEditor Javascript library
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Charles", "Bordet", , "charles@datachamp.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The SunEditor Javascript library is a WYSIWYG web editor, with no
    dependencies. This package provides a set of functions to use it in R. It
    allows you to transform a textarea into a WYSIWYG editor.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
